; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests auto transaction posting where amount_expr evaluates to a long
; integer or a non-amount type. When amount_expr returns is_long(), it
; must be converted via to_amount().

= /Expenses:Food/
    (Budget:Food)             (2)

2024/01/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food              $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal
             $-50.00  Assets:Cash
             $100.00  Budget:Food
              $50.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
             $100.00
end test
